# mkisofs

##### create iso image from a directory

   mkisofs  -o XYZ.iso XYZ/

##### Make ISO image of a folder

   mkisofs  -J -allow-lowercase -R -V "OpenCD8806" -iso-level 4 -o OpenCD.iso ~/OpenCD

